          "cookies": [],
          "content": {
            "size": 7163,
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "text": "{\"first_sign\":{\"id\":1,\"type\":\"zodiac\",\"sign\":\"aquarius\",\"element_id\":4,\"modality_id\":6,\"polarity_id\":8,\"ruling_planet_id\":10,\"element\":{\"id\":4,\"type\":\"element\",\"code\":\"air\",\"created_at\":\"2022-06-15 12:30:50\",\"updated_at\":\"2022-06-15 12:30:50\"}},\"second_sign\":{\"id\":12,\"type\":\"zodiac\",\"sign\":\"capricorn\",\"element_id\":1,\"modality_id\":5,\"polarity_id\":9,\"ruling_planet_id\":10,\"element\":{\"id\":1,\"type\":\"element\",\"code\":\"earth\",\"created_at\":\"2022-06-15 12:30:50\",\"updated_at\":\"2022-06-15 12:30:50\"}},\"overview\":\"Capricorn and Aquarius share a strong sense of ambition and have mutual respect for each other's goals and dreams. They can both be quite stubborn and set in their ways, but they usually learn to compromise and support each other in their efforts. Furthermore, they both enjoy intellectual conversations and can provide each other with interesting perspectives.\",\"compatibilityLevel\":{\"name\":\"Meaningful connection\",\"percent\":60,\"description\":\"Bring out the best in each other\"},\"wheel_of_balance_sexual_percent\":50,\"wheelOfBalanceSexualLevel\":{\"name\":\"Medium\",\"description\":\"These two are both passionate and playful during sex, but their relationship can be superficial and short-lasting. The problem they might have to deal with is the lack of emotional bond. Without connecting on a deeper level, this relationship can fizzle out in time.\",\"type\":\"sexual\"},\"wheel_of_balance_intellectual_percent\":85,\"wheelOfBalanceIntellectualLevel\":{\"name\":\"Very high\",\"description\":\"These two are a knock-out intellectual match. Both enjoy exploring new things, are curious, and have an adventurous spirit. They keep each other mentally stimulated, and their romantic connection thrives because of this consistent spark.\",\"type\":\"intellectual\"},\"wheel_of_balance_emotional_percent\":50,\"wheelOfBalanceEmotionalLevel\":{\"name\":\"Medium\",\"description\":\"Connecting on an emotional level is one area this couple may struggle with. They are both not used to processing their feelings or expressing them, which ultimately can make their communication pretty shallow. If both partners learn to get in touch with their emotions and vocalize them without judgment, this relationship is fated to last.\",\"type\":\"emotional\"},\"wheel_of_balance_spiritual_percent\":60,\"wheelOfBalanceSpiritualLevel\":{\"name\":\"High\",\"description\":\"This is a couple that could talk for hours — and they absolutely will! These two fundamentally understand each other even though, on the surface, their personalities are not alike. They have enough similarities to get along nicely but enough differences to find one another fascinating.\",\"type\":\"spiritual\"},\"toxicity_score_percent\":25,\"toxicityScoreLevel\":{\"name\":\"Mild\",\"description\":\"These two can get moody at times, so misunderstandings are common. To resolve conflicts, they should work on being more sensitive to one another's emotions: hear each other out and discuss differences calmly and respectfully.\"},\"compatibility_aspects_love_percent\":55,\"compatibility_aspects_love_description\":\"While these two both have strong personalities and share a mutual appreciation of intelligence, Capricorn tends to be more traditional and conservative, while Aquarius is more independent and non-conforming. This can cause tension between the two as Capricorn may feel stifled or constrained by Aquarius's free-spirited attitude.\",\"compatibility_aspects_marriage_percent\":70,\"compatibility_aspects_marriage_description\":\"Capricorn and Aquarius are both capable of forming a stable and satisfying union. They have very different approaches to romance, but their differences can be complementary. Capricorns are traditionalists who take relationships seriously and need stability, while Aquarians are spontaneous and can bring a lot of excitement and adventure into their pairing. \",\"compatibility_aspects_trust_percent\":70,\"compatibilityAspectsTrustLevel\":{\"name\":\"High\",\"description\":\"These two base their relationship on respect and honesty. Reliable, faithful, and loving partners, this duo will be each other’s back in the hardest of times. Even if they have misunderstandings in other areas of their relationship, they would hardly betray each other’s trust.\"},\"compatibility_aspects_teamwork_percent\":50,\"compatibilityAspectsTeamworkLevel\":{\"name\":\"Medium\",\"description\":\"These two understand each other’s personalities and are willing to work together toward shared goals. They may struggle with competitiveness at times, but once they align their ambitions and priorities, there’s nothing this driven couple can’t accomplish.\"},\"compatibility_aspects_communication_percent\":55,\"compatibilityAspectsCommunicationLevel\":{\"name\":\"Medium\",\"description\":\"These two are both direct and prefer to address problems head-on. Even though they can be blunt and quick-tempered, neither partner is mean-spirited or holds grudges, so they quickly get over emotional outbursts. As long as they communicate their needs and boundaries openly, they can build a fulfilling relationship.\"},\"compatibility_aspects_humor_percent\":85,\"compatibilityAspectsHumorLevel\":{\"name\":\"High\",\"description\":\"These two never get bored with each other. Being fun-loving and witty, they tend to turn everything into a game and constantly make each other laugh. They have a ton of inside jokes and won’t think twice about dragging each other on exciting adventures.\"},\"biggestChallenges\":[{\"name\":\"Ineffective arguments\",\"description\":\"Disagreements can be helpful or destructive, depending on what you do with them. Having the same fight over and over, losing your temper, or saying things you regret later is bound to make you feel it’s not worth it.\",\"solution\":\"A good fight is one after which you have agreed on what can be the first step both will take to resolve the issue. Start by listening to hear the other side, not only by waiting for your turn. Research together ways to fight better and only ever focus on the next step needed to take.\"},{\"name\":\"Poor communication\",\"description\":\"Poor communication leads to misunderstandings, fights, and frustration. It also leads to one or both of you feeling unheard and invalidated and can quickly build into resentment and other common relationship issues.\",\"solution\":\"Communication is a skill like any other, and learning it can make all the difference to your relationship. Learn how to listen without judging or interrupting, and how to get your point across without attacking.\"},{\"name\":\"Growing apart\",\"description\":\"So many things on the task list, and there is only one of you. How long ago did you stop including things to do with your partner on that list? Drifting apart happens bit by bit, and we don’t notice. You might wake up one morning and realize you can’t remember the last time you had sex, a date, or a conversation that is more than organizational.\",\"solution\":\"A relationship is like a flower, and it can not blossom without nourishment. When you notice the signs, it is time to act. It will take time to cross the distance that has been created, but it is possible. Prioritize your time together, bring back old habits and activities you did together, laugh, and take time to reconnect.\"}]}"
          },
